                     <title>Asmat prayers against enemies, based on a collection of Psalms; </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>  ብከ፡ ንወግዖሙ፡ ለኵሎሙ፡ ፀርነ። በስመ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>  ወበስምከ፡ ነኃሥሮሙ፡ ለእለ፡ ቆሙ፡ ላዕሌነ፡ በስመ፡ አብ፡</incipit>
                     <note>for instance, made up of the lines of Psalm 43:5ff, interspersed with an abbreviated form of the Trinitarian formula, e.g., በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወ፡ ወመ፡</note>

